Book containing Bryson Shahn's contacts, phone numbers, and addresses, organized alphabetically and heavily embellished with color pencil illustrations. Shahn occasionally also includes appointments, reminders, birthdays, and notes to self. Latest dated entry reads "the end of March, 2002."
Book is a pre-printed diary with full-page black and white reproductions of works by Marino Marini, some of which have been drawn over by Bryson Shahn.
Archives of American Art, Smithsonian Institution
